_sText: OK here's a reupload of glass_cells.  Included in the .zip file are glass_cellsbeta1 and glass_cellsbeta2.  Beta1 is fullbright, Beta2 has 'proper' lighting.  I prefer the fullbright version because, well, it's easy to see everything.  But some might prefer Beta2 with its hanging spotlights.  Everything is still cell shaded.
